title: ‘The Challenge: USA’ Episode 6 | Surviving the Challenge
description:
Tyson and Amelia break down the latest episode of 'The Challenge: USA.' They talk about the fallout from last week’s elimination challenge, the difficulty of this week’s challenge, and how much danger Tyson was really in heading into the elimination challenge.

Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Amelia Wedemeyer
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
